Please install it following these steps :

1. Install tur-repo & dvc-repo
pkg i tur-repo -y & pkg i dichvucoder-repo -y
2. Remove php & tur-repo
pkg remove tur-repo php* -y
3. Install php :
PHP 7.2 :
pkg i php7.2 -y
PHP 7.4 :
pkg i php7 -y
PHP 8.1 :
pkg i php-8.1 -y
4. Install Dichvucoder extension:
PHP 7.2 :
pkg i php7.2-dichvucoder -y
PHP 7.4 :
pkg i php7-dichvucoder -y
PHP 8.1 :
pkg i php-8.1-dichvucoder -y

So you have succeeded in installing the Dichvucoder extension.
Now you can run the tool normally.
